Package org.net4care.storage

This package contains classes that define the storage and external feeder systems on the server side.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExternalDataSource
    Interface to External data sources (feeder systems) for CPR and person data; and EHR that has treatment data.
    ObservationCache
    Interface to an server side cache of observation for fast retrieval in the serialized on-the-wire format of the stored StandardTeleObservations.
    TreatmentData
    The data of a treatment (behandling).
    XDSQuery
    A marker interface.
    XDSRepository
    Interface to an XDS repository for storing HL7 documents.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddressData
    Data on an address.
    PersonData
    Data for a person: address, telephone, gender, birthtime, etc.
    RegistryEntry
    A data container for the meta data that defines an entry in the XDS registry.

Package org.net4care.storage Description

This package contains classes that define the storage and external feeder systems on the server side.

The interfaces and classes within this package are only for Net4Care framework developers, not for developers of home telemedical applications.
